videos.headline: Bateman leaps for the 19-yard TD catch
videos.description: Rashod Bateman does a flying leap in the end zone to haul in a 19-yard touchdown from Tanner Morgan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Bateman leaps for the 19-yard TD catch) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brooks goes 9 yards for an easy TD
videos.description: Shannon Brooks gets the quick handoff, finds an opening toward the corner and runs in the nine-yard Minnesota touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Brooks goes 9 yards for an easy TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bateman makes another toe-tapping TD
videos.description: Tanner Morgan connects with Rashod Bateman for another Minnesota touchdown, this time for 10 yards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Bateman makes another toe-tapping TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Northwestern's James comes down with the one-handed TD catch
videos.description: While being held by his defender, Jace James gets a hand free and pulls down the nine-yard touchdown catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Northwestern's James comes down with the one-handed TD catch) 2019/11/23 ESHEET
